ArbitraryLines
===============


AbritraryLines is an Eclipse plugin which allows you to configure arbitrary
lines in the editor. You can configure:

 * Direction (vertical or horizontal)
 * Location (pixel or character offset)
 * Thickness
 * Color (including transparency)
 * Offset


License
